node.text:
Had a blast the other day when @mamadou_ndiaye34 visited The Zoo 🙌 the only problem is he made my big snake look tiny 🐍 and my big lizard look like a gecko 🦎 still not sure how that giant chicken leg looked so small when he fed it 🍗 but we had a great time regardless ✌️
.
.
.

node.text:
The Everglades are truly an amazing place 🙌 but very few are explore in the dark 🌙 and that’s when you can see some crazy things 😱 Juliette and I saw some incredible animals in just a short period of time and wow am I glad to share it with you all 🙏
.
.
.

node.text:
When the big reticulated pythons lay their eggs 🥚 the best thing for the babies and the mom is to remove the eggs 🤷‍♂️ this is because the babies get a higher chance at successfully hatching 🐣 and the mom gets to go back to her normal life quicker 🐍 of course mama doesn’t know I’m trying to help 😬 which can make it interesting 😂 
.
.
.

.
.
.

.

node.text:
The Everglades are truly an amazing place 🙌 but very few are explore in the dark 🌙 and that’s when you can see some crazy things 😱 Juliette and I saw some incredible animals in just a short period of time and wow am I glad to share it with you all 🙏
.
.
.
